Changes file for OPM::Maker
===========================

1.10 2021-10-01 17:11:00

  + added support for huge files (see #7)
  + Use OPM::Validate to validate opm files
  + improve support for other ticketing systems

1.00 2021-03-13 11:21:00

  + Renamed OTRS::OPM::Maker to OPM::Maker as it supports OPM building for other ticketing systems (e.g. Znuny and OTOBO) as well

